<topic id="ant-quick-assist">
  <title>Ant Quick Assist Support</title>
  <body>
    <p>The <term>Quick Assist</term> support helps you to rapidly access search and refactoring
      actions. If one or more actions are available in the current context, they are accessible via
      a yellow bulb icon (<image href="../img/QuickAssist16.png"/>) placed at the current line in
      the stripe on the left side of the editor. Also, you can invoke the quick assist menu by using
      the <uicontrol><shortcut>Alt + 1</shortcut></uicontrol> (<uicontrol><shortcut>Meta + Alt +
          1</shortcut></uicontrol> on Mac OS X) keyboard shortcuts.</p>
